{"tid":652687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭中基斥港府：母語係咩都問人","createTime":"2018-05-04T04:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T13:51:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f75f202c8ab99b07f08de4780dcb3d7ae646c897","tid":652687,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180504/20380617?_ga=2.42884517.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F20380617%3F_ga%3D2.42884517.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171&d=Sd1MjDIViAuoschmB10ygBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=bab279d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F20380617%3F_ga%3D2.42884517.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171&h=86c6545c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180504/20380617?_ga=2.42884517.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月04日 <br />\n<br />\n鄭中基斥港府：母語係咩都問人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180504/large/a0802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180504%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=04f68328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】甚麼是母語？特首林鄭月娥認為是無聊問題，教育局局長楊潤雄一度連回答也不敢。藝人鄭中基則於兩周內兩度發文炮轟港府及楊潤雄，「點解連母語係咩都要問人？仲要問個講國語嘅人，你唔好問個西人？」他指廣東話是香港人母語，根本沒有爭拗餘地，「你點樣做教育局長？你辭職啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤爆粗鬧教局<br />\n<br />\n廣東話被內地學者貶為非香港人母語，港府拒清楚表述立場。藝人鄭中基昨在facebook發炮，「你細個阿媽點教你講說話？你依（𠵱）家係點樣諗嘢？用咩語言邏輯？」他又落hashtag暗諷：「#我都問咗個賣牛雜嘅學者佢話大家個母語係廣東話喎」。<br />\n<br />\n教育局早前收緊中學歷史課本的內容審查，鄭中基早已發文狠批：「教育局長嚟講一蟹臭過一蟹」，昨再斥楊潤雄不配做教育局局長，「你辭職啦」。一向敢言的藝人杜汶澤前晚也在facebook表態，「教育局你噏乜X啫？其實如果粵語唔係你嘅母語，咁我X你老母你都唔知我講乜啦！」<br />\n<br />\n另一藝人黃秋生昨則引述「封神榜上古漢語配音」短片，指上古漢語即先秦至漢朝使用的漢語，才是正宗漢人母語，「以後便用這種語言上課罷（吧）。不可爭議不休，呢個係一個無聊問題」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王家文  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n指廣東話爭議無風起浪轟議員問題無聊　林鄭「三次不認母語」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n前教育局長轟製造社會矛盾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前教育局長轟製造社會矛盾<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果照相機】林鄭講嘢議員做乜好？<br />\n<br />\n指廣東話爭議無風起浪　轟議員問題無聊林鄭「三次不認母語」"},{"pid":"79b885e733fefd7c031f65ce1a94d6c53cdcaa2f","tid":652687,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc628a7ee96968580e1acd1d008d7c34c155e07","tid":652687,"uid":107990,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"林病唔敢答啦<br />\n度度都怕得罪"},{"pid":"7db33d0eeb5e95807ceb33fc3d1696e271199653","tid":652687,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/131214_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai